Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "a" range [0.3, ) values "b" range [0.3, )
values "gs_resol" range [3,)
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, enable2dDetLevels = 2+4+8+16+32
if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType"
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Detailed`,`Simple`,`Off` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Off` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Simple` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else gs_detlevel_3D = `Detailed` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Off` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Simple` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
VALUES "gs_leg_type" stLegType VALUES "gs_leg_type_m" 1,2,3,4,5
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_leg_type" THEN gs_leg_type_m = 1 FOR i = 2 TO 5 IF gs_leg_type = stLegType[i] THEN gs_leg_type_m = i NEXT i PARAMETERS gs_leg_type_m = gs_leg_type_m ELSE gs_leg_type = stLegType[gs_leg_type_m] PARAMETERS gs_leg_type = gs_leg_type ENDIF
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_seat_height" THEN zzyzx = gs_seat_height + zzDist PARAMETERS zzyzx = gs_seat_height + zzDist ELSE PARAMETERS zzDist = zzyzx - gs_seat_height ENDIF
VALUES "gs_seat_height" RANGE[0.43,)
!!! ******************************** Minimal Space
VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSSide" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSRear" RANGE [0,)
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS=0.001 UnID = 1 numfoot=5 bDetailed=0
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then bDetailed=1 Leglength = gs_seat_height-0.32 !!! majd az ulesmagassag allitja
gs_OrigoCentered = 0
dim stSymbolTypes[16] stSymbolTypes[ 1] = `Circle` stSymbolTypes[ 2] = `Circle with Backrest` stSymbolTypes[ 3] = `Rectangle` stSymbolTypes[ 4] = `Rectangle with Backrest 1` stSymbolTypes[ 5] = `Trapezoid` stSymbolTypes[ 6] = `Trapezoid with Backrest` stSymbolTypes[ 7] = `Curved` stSymbolTypes[ 8] = `Curved with Backrest` stSymbolTypes[ 9] = `Rectangle with Backrest 3` stSymbolTypes[10] = `Rectangle with Backrest 2` stSymbolTypes[11] = `Circle with Backrest 2` stSymbolTypes[12] = `Circle with Backrest 3` stSymbolTypes[13] = `Curved with Backrest 2` stSymbolTypes[14] = `Curved with Backrest 3` stSymbolTypes[15] = `Detailed 1` stSymbolTypes[16] = `Detailed 2`
